{"word":"H8041 - שָׂמַאל - sâmaʼl - saw-mal' - Left - இடது","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>שָׂמַאל"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>sâmaʼl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>saw-mal'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Left / இடது"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இடதுபக்கம். இடதுபுறம்போ, இடது புறமாய் சாய், இடதுகை, இடதுபுறமாக வெட்டு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to take the left, to go to the left (Hiphil)"},{"paragraph":"1) to go to the left"},{"paragraph":"2) to turn (aside) to the left (figurative)"},{"paragraph":"3) to use the left hand"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root (rather denominative from <a href=\"#/H8040 - שְׂמֹאול - sᵉmôʼwl - sem-ole'/8040\">H8040</a>); to use the <i>left</i> hand or pass in that direction: - (go, turn) (on the, to the) left."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8040 - שְׂמֹאול - sᵉmôʼwl - sem-ole'/8040\">H8040</a>, <a href=\"#/H8041 - שָׂמַאל - sâmaʼl - saw-mal'/8041\">H8041</a>, <a href=\"#/H8042 - שְׂמָאלִי - sᵉmâʼlîy - sem-aw-lee'/8042\">H8042</a>"}]}